Tags.string 'NodeComment': Start Location Trigger can be edited via the exposed, instance editable reference variable. When that is triggered we call Move to Start Location

The elevator is another example of how to use the triggers.
It has two locations and two triggers we mapped so the elevator goes between them.
We do the same with End Location Trigger and Move to End Location. Note this is done with the button in mind.
When the pawn overlaps, we move either to the start or end location
A timeline is used to drive the elevator either to the start or end location. When finished we update the IsAtEndLocation boolean.
